    "parse": {
      "title": "Ostrich",
      "pageid": 11874,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Ostrich\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"Ostrich.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/ad/Ostrich.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"93\" height=\"96\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Adult ostriches will lay a very large egg once a week.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Barn.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/24px-Barn.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/36px-Barn.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/48px-Barn.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">N/A\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Ostrich</b> is an <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>. Ostriches can be hatched by placing an <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a> into an <a href=\"/Ostrich_Incubator\" title=\"Ostrich Incubator\">Ostrich Incubator</a>, taking <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 15,000m (9d 10h)</span> to incubate, or <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 7,500m (4d 18h 20m)</span> with the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Coopmaster Profession</a>.\n</p><p>An Ostrich Egg can be initially found by solving <a href=\"/Journal_Scraps#Journal_Scrap_.2310\" title=\"Journal Scraps\">Journal Scrap #10</a>, or as a random drop from the chests in the <a href=\"/Volcano_Dungeon\" title=\"Volcano Dungeon\">Volcano Dungeon</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ostrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Ostriches who eat every day mature after 7 nights have passed. A mature and fed Ostrich produces an <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a> every 7 days. An Ostrich Egg can be placed in an <a href=\"/Ostrich_Incubator\" title=\"Ostrich Incubator\">Ostrich Incubator</a> to hatch another ostrich, or sold for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"600\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />600g</span>.\n</p><p>An Ostrich Egg can be placed in a <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> to produce 10 <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> of the same quality as the egg.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Ostrich_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>\n</td>\n<td>It may be the world's largest egg.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>600g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>750g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>900g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>1,200g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ostrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It is possible to sell Ostriches. The selling price is dependent on how many <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">hearts</a> the animal has (<span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"20800\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />20,800g</span> max).\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ostrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Introduced.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413221127\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.095 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2640/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9381/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 943/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3424/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 582 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   69.556      1 -total\n 43.04%   29.938      1 Template:Infobox_animal\n 31.99%   22.250      1 Template:Qualityprice\n 30.64%   21.313      2 Template:Description\n 13.88%    9.656      2 Template:Name\n  9.75%    6.784      4 Template:Overlayimg\n  6.52%    4.534      2 Template:Duration\n  3.61%    2.509      1 Template:History\n  2.77%    1.925      2 Template:Price\n  2.30%    1.600      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:11874-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413221127 and revision id 190522\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = Ostrich.png\n|building = {{Name|Barn}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Ostrich Egg}}\n}}\nThe '''Ostrich''' is an [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Barn]]. Ostriches can be hatched by placing an [[Ostrich Egg]] into an [[Ostrich Incubator]], taking {{duration|15,000m (9d 10h)|class=inline}} to incubate, or {{duration|7,500m (4d 18h 20m)|class=inline}} with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]].\n\nAn Ostrich Egg can be initially found by solving [[Journal Scraps#Journal Scrap #10|Journal Scrap #10]], or as a random drop from the chests in the [[Volcano Dungeon]].\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nOstriches who eat every day mature after 7 nights have passed. A mature and fed Ostrich produces an [[Ostrich Egg]] every 7 days. An Ostrich Egg can be placed in an [[Ostrich Incubator]] to hatch another ostrich, or sold for {{Price|600}}.\n\nAn Ostrich Egg can be placed in a [[Mayonnaise Machine]] to produce 10 [[Mayonnaise]] of the same quality as the egg.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Ostrich Egg.png]]\n|[[Ostrich Egg]]\n|{{Description|Ostrich Egg}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Ostrich Egg|600|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Selling==\nIt is possible to sell Ostriches. The selling price is dependent on how many [[Animals#Friendship|hearts]] the animal has ({{Price|20800}} max).\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Barn animals]]\n\n[[de:Strauß]]\n[[es:Avestruz]]\n[[fr:Autruche]]\n[[it:Struzzo]]\n[[ja:ダチョウ]]\n[[ko:타조]]\n[[hu:Strucc]]\n[[pt:Avestruz]]\n[[ru:Страус]]\n[[tr:Deve Kuşu]]\n[[zh:鸵鸟]]"
